fields.Title: LAIR / INSTIGATORS TENT
fields.Description:
1. Find Ruby's journal here.
2. Use to stow away Ruby's body if she killed herself.

fields.Title: Instigator's Tent: "Assorted softcovers, mostly pulp ho..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Assorted softcovers, mostly pulp horror. A motor carriage lies buried in the snow on one cover, on another -- a ghost airship. You also see a collection of radio enthusiast magazines.

fields.Title: Savoir Faire: "It was pitched by practised hands -..."
fields.Dialogue Text: It was pitched by practised hands -- she's used to camping out.

fields.Title: You: ""A notebook." (Take it.)"
fields.Dialogue Text: "A notebook." (Take it.)

fields.Title: Instigator's Tent: "There she lies, cocooned in the sle..."
fields.Dialogue Text: There she lies, cocooned in the sleeping bag, surrounded by empty cigarette packs, books, and half-read magazines.

fields.Title: Inland Empire: "She watches by, motionless."
fields.Dialogue Text: She watches by, motionless.

fields.Title: Perception (Smell): "It reeks of cigarettes."
fields.Dialogue Text: It reeks of cigarettes.

fields.Title: Jump to: [Instigator's Tent: "The plain red tent rests stoically..."]
Instigator's Tent: "The tent looks old but well-maintai..."
fields.Dialogue Text: The tent looks old but well-maintained. In the darkness of the tent -- a rolled-up sleeping bag, cooking utensils, some books and a kerosene lamp.

fields.Title: Instigator's Tent: "The plain red tent rests stoically..."
fields.Dialogue Text: The plain red tent rests stoically in the corner.

fields.Title: You: "Look at the books."
fields.Dialogue Text: Look at the books.
fields.Alternate1: Shine your flashlight on the books.

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""We should put her in the sleeping..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "We should put her in the sleeping bag so the rats don't get to her."

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""We should read this *immediately*...."
fields.Dialogue Text: "We should read this *immediately*. Like -- right now."

fields.Title: You: "Look inside."
fields.Dialogue Text: Look inside.

dialogueEntries.conditionsString: Variable["boardwalk.ruby_killed_herself"]  and  Variable["boardwalk.tent_covered"] == false  and  Variable["TASK.read_ruby_journal"] == false

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: "The lieutenant nods."
fields.Dialogue Text: The lieutenant nods.

fields.Title: You: "Take the notebook."
fields.Dialogue Text: Take the notebook.

fields.Title: Savoir Faire: "It was pitched by practised hands -..."
fields.Dialogue Text: It was pitched by practised hands -- she was used to camping out.

fields.Title: You: "Sift through the magazines."
fields.Dialogue Text: Sift through the magazines.

fields.Title: You: "[Leave.]"
fields.Dialogue Text: [Leave.]

fields.Title: Instigator's Tent: "The instigator's body has been remo..."
fields.Dialogue Text: The instigator's body has been removed by Processing. The tent seems orphaned now.

fields.Title: Logic: "Magazines? You should look through..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Magazines? You should look through them.

fields.Title: You: "Back out of the tent."
fields.Dialogue Text: Back out of the tent.

fields.Title: Instigator's Tent: "You pocket the worn brown leather j..."
fields.Dialogue Text: You pocket the worn brown leather journal.

fields.Title: Instigator's Tent: "'Rega Monthly', 'Journal of Materia..."
fields.Dialogue Text: 'Rega Monthly', 'Journal of Material Science'. More technological digest. One of the magazines doesn't have images on the cover -- it's not a magazine, it's a leather notebook!

fields.Title: You: "Look inside."
fields.Dialogue Text: Look inside.

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""See anything?" The lieutenant peek..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "See anything?" The lieutenant peeks in over your shoulder.

fields.Title: You: "Sift through the books and magazine..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Sift through the books and magazines.
fields.Alternate1: Shine your flashlight on the books and magazines.

fields.Title: Instigator's Tent: "You see a rolled-up sleeping bag an..."
fields.Dialogue Text: You see a rolled-up sleeping bag and personal belongings.

fields.Title: Instigator's Tent: "The plain red tent rests stoically..."
fields.Dialogue Text: The plain red tent rests stoically in the corner. Ruby's dead body is wrapped in her sleeping bag.

fields.Title: You: ""Okay, let's carry her over here.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Okay, let's carry her over here."

fields.Title: Inland Empire: "A trusted friend left behind..."
fields.Dialogue Text: A trusted friend left behind...

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""I see the processing guys have bee..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "I see the processing guys have been faster than usual. It's good we stopped by to check regardless." He nods at the lack of Ruby in the tent, then looks around. "Now -- island time."

fields.Title: Jump to: [Instigator's Tent: "Assorted softcovers, mostly pulp ho..."]
Instigator's Tent: "In the darkness of the tent: Ruby's..."
fields.Dialogue Text: In the darkness of the tent: Ruby's body, zipped up in her sleeping bag. Next to the body -- some books and a kerosene lamp.

fields.Title: Esprit de Corps: "You'll need the lieutenant's help t..."
fields.Dialogue Text: You'll need the lieutenant's help to carry her over.

fields.Title: Instigator's Tent: "The plain red tent rests stoically..."
fields.Dialogue Text: The plain red tent rests stoically in the corner.

fields.Title: Instigator's Tent: "The plain red tent stands by dispas..."
fields.Dialogue Text: The plain red tent stands by dispassionately.
